OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by #21 from
OL,4,CJanuary after second winter price cap
OL,5,Cincrease
OL,7,FThe average household energy bill is
OL,8,Fset to rise again from January, as
OL,9,FOfgem announced a 1.2% increase to the
OL,10,Fenergy price cap.
OL,12,FThis is the regulator's second
OL,13,Fconsecutive rise this winter, after
OL,14,Fthe price cap increased by 10% in
OL,15,FOctober.
OL,17,FOfgem said average household bills
OL,18,Fwill rise by #21 a year or around
OL,19,F#1.75 per month.
