OL,7,F"So it's more important than ever to
OL,8,Fstay focused on building a renewable,
OL,9,Fhome-grown energy system to bring
OL,10,Fcosts down and give households
OL,11,Fstability."
OL,13,FIt comes as millions of pensioners are
OL,14,Falso facing a winter with less
OL,15,Fsupport, after the new government
OL,16,Fscrapped winter fuel payments for
OL,17,Fthose who do not receive pension
OL,18,Fcredit or other benefits.
