OL,7,FAbout 10 million pensioners will miss
OL,8,Fout on the payments of up to #300 this
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FDespite the increases, prices are
OL,12,Fexpected to fall slightly in both the
OL,13,Fsecond and fourth quarters of next
OL,14,Fyear, according to energy consultancy
OL,15,FCornwall Insight.
OL,17,FOfgem changes the price cap for
OL,18,Fhouseholds every three months, largely
OL,19,Fbased on the cost of energy on
OL,20,Fwholesale markets.
