OL,7,FOfgem is also currently considering
OL,8,Fthe future of price protection,
OL,9,Fincluding the suitability of the price
OL,10,Fcap and a potential permanent ban on
OL,11,Fso-called acquisition tariffs `
OL,12,Fcheaper prices for new customers to
OL,13,Flure them away from their existing
OL,14,Fsupplier.
OL,16,FCharities have voiced their concerns
OL,17,Fover another price rise, with National
OL,18,FEnergy Action saying the current cold
OL,19,Fspell was already having a devastating
OL,20,Fimpact on the most vulnerable people.
