OL,8,Fdisability equality charity Scope,
OL,9,Fsaid: "This is a bitter pill to
OL,10,Fswallow for the many disabled people
OL,11,Fwho face sky-high bills because they
OL,12,Fhave no choice but to use more energy.
OL,14,F"Life costs a lot more when you're
OL,15,Fdisabled, because of needing to use
OL,16,Fmore heating to stay warm and healthy,
OL,17,For charging vital equipment like
OL,18,Fwheelchairs and breathing machines.
